content: --कुमार {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {1} very delicate or soft, smooth. {2} beautifully young or youthful. (--रः {1} a beautiful youth. {2} a kind of sugar-cane. {3} a kind of grain (श्यामाक). {4} a kind of mustard. {5} the wild Campaka. (--रा {1} the double jasmine. {2} the plantain. {3} the great-flowered jasmine.
